summary:
I have complicated my BSc. in Chemistry and masters (MSc.) in Organic Chemistry from Department of Chemistry, Guwahati University. I have completed my research leading to Ph.D (bioinorganic chemistry) from Ewha Womans University, Seoul South Korea. Currently I am work as a post doctoral researcher in organic synthesis at the University of Groningen. 

My expertise are in analysis and trapping intermediates in various chemical reaction to understand the mechanisms. My research interest is in exploring various reactions to follow and understand reactions pathways. I have keen interest to collaborate within different fields of chemistry leading to the development of new methodologies and exploring in the field of photoinduced reaction pathways.
